WEBVTT

00:06:00.068 --> 00:06:02.044
Y'all don't know that? Protect and serve.

00:06:02.068 --> 00:06:03.069
(Laughter)

00:06:03.093 --> 00:06:04.498
So you look at the other arm,

00:06:04.522 --> 00:06:06.657
and then you look at it
and ... there it is.

00:06:06.681 --> 00:06:07.854
(Laughter)

00:06:08.267 --> 00:06:10.156
You know, it's kinda weak.

00:06:10.926 --> 00:06:12.163
It looks sickly.

00:06:12.972 --> 00:06:14.758
It's withering and it's dying

00:06:15.861 --> 00:06:18.504
because we've invested so much
in our protective arm.

00:06:19.302 --> 00:06:22.159
But we forgot to treat our communities

00:06:22.183 --> 00:06:23.566
like they're our customers;

00:06:24.026 --> 00:06:26.991
like they're our sons and daughters,
our brothers and sisters,

00:06:27.015 --> 00:06:28.205
our mothers and fathers.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:30.849
And so somehow, along the way,